th systems. Unlock various enhancements through repeated runs for easier and more exciting battles. The game also features abundant cosmetic skins and accessories for character customization.<br><br><br><br><strong>Game Contents:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 different playable characters (more to be unlocked!)<br></li><li>13 Levels with at least 36 random generated maps<br></li><li>10+ Bosses and many different enemies<br></li><li>300+ Powers, runes, items and enhanced abilities<br></li><li>Various customizable skins<br></li><li>We will keep updating more!</li></ul>","developers":["Moju Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088650/header.jpg?t=1729238511","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256981857,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256981857/movie480.mp4?t=1699850780","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256981857/movie_max.mp4?t=1699850780"},"name":"New Mist Walker - Swordsman","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256981857/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1699850780","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256981857/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1699850780","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256981857/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1699850780"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256963991,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256963991/movie480.mp4?t=1692197530","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256963991/movie_max.mp4?t=1692197530"},"name":"Mist Slayer Launch Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256963991/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1692197530","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256963991/movie480_vp9.webm?t=169